    problem: `Most fintech products assume users want dashboards, menus, and forms. For users across Nigeria, Ghana, Tanzania, and South Africa — many interacting with digital finance for the first time — that assumption fails completely. The real insight: everyone already knows how to have a conversation.`,
    aiAngle: `I designed and implemented an AI orchestration layer that converts free-form natural language — "I want to send 50k to my sister's GTB account" — into a structured, validated, executed financial transaction. No forms. No menus. The AI understands intent, extracts entities, resolves ambiguity, and executes.`,
