    problem: `Staking platforms speak in APY percentages, lock-up periods, validator risk scores, and protocol terminology. For the majority of users — who understand that they want their money to grow, but not the mechanics of how — this creates a massive comprehension gap that leads to poor decisions, abandoned onboarding, and churn.`,
